      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 42.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 42.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>強梁者不得其死，吾將以為教父。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What other men (thus) teach, I also teach. The violent and strong do not die their natural death. I will make this the basis of my teaching.</seg>
      </tuv>
